	measure TotalCostOFGoodsSold_PMTD = ```
			
			// VAR TodayDate = TODAY()
			VAR TodayDate=[TodayLocal]
			VAR CurrentDay = DAY(TodayDate)
			VAR CurrentMonth = MONTH(TodayDate)
			VAR CurrentYear = YEAR(TodayDate)
			
			VAR PrevMonth = IF(CurrentMonth = 1, 12, CurrentMonth - 1)
			VAR PrevYear = IF(CurrentMonth = 1, CurrentYear - 1, CurrentYear)
			
			VAR StartDate = DATE(PrevYear, PrevMonth, 1)
			VAR EndDate = DATE(PrevYear, PrevMonth, CurrentDay)
			
			RETURN
			    CALCULATE(
			        generalLedgerEntries[TotalCostOFGoodsSold],
			       generalLedgerEntries[postingDate] >= StartDate,
			        generalLedgerEntries[postingDate] <= EndDate
			    )
			
			```
		displayFolder: CostOfGoodsSold
